# Design System

All design tokens are centralized in `src/styles/variables.scss`.

## Color System (HSL)
Based on shadcn/ui design system:

```scss
$primary: hsl(222.2, 47.4%, 11.2%);
$primary-foreground: hsl(210, 40%, 98%);
$secondary: hsl(210, 40%, 96.1%);
$destructive: hsl(0, 84.2%, 60.2%);
$border: hsl(214.3, 31.8%, 91.4%);
$ring: hsl(222.2, 84%, 4.9%);
```

## Spacing Scale
- `$spacing-xs`: 0.25rem (4px)
- `$spacing-sm`: 0.5rem (8px)
- `$spacing-md`: 1rem (16px)
- `$spacing-lg`: 1.5rem (24px)
- `$spacing-xl`: 2rem (32px)

## Border Radius
- `$radius-xs` to `$radius-xl` (0.25rem to 1rem)

## Typography
- Font family: `$font-sans` (system fonts)
- Sizes: `$font-size-xs` to `$font-size-xl` (0.75rem to 1.25rem)

## Transitions
- `$transition-fast`: 150ms (hover effects)
- `$transition-base`: 200ms (default)
- `$transition-slow`: 300ms (complex animations)

## Usage Rule
Always import variables: `@import '../../styles/variables.scss';`
